---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="UTS Professional Review | Dylan Purbrick" activeTab="uni">
  <div class="max-w-4xl">
    <header class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-brand-purple font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4">// Internal_Audit</p>
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-industrial-black">
            Professional <span class="text-brand-orange italic font-wayfinder lowercase">Review</span>
        </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-20 font-neue">
        <section class="bg-white/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
            <h2 class="text-brand-purple font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-6">Peer Feedback Summary</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Reflecting on my collaboration with Olivia, Muhaimin, and Eric, our team focused on the mechanical structure of a mechatronic system. Key takeaways included the importance of bridging the gap between technical CAD modeling and cost-effective material procurement.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-brand-orange mb-2">Technical Insight</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">My role at Keith Engineering allowed me to bring industry-standard QA practices to our student project, specifically in BOM verification.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase text-brand-orange mb-2">Team Leadership</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Applied supervisor-level team management skills developed at the Lord Dudley Hotel to maintain project milestones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-industrial-black font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-8">Reflective Practice</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-slate text-slate-600">
                <p>
                    As a final-year Mechatronic Engineering student at UTS, this portfolio serves as evidence of my ability to transition from theoretical modeling to practical, industrial-grade implementation.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
